Package: fastconley
Type: Package
Title: Fast Conley Standard Errors for felm() Models
Version: 0.3.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Richard", "Bluhm", email = "richard.bluhm@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: Richard Bluhm <richard.bluhm@gmail.com>
Description: Conley (1997) spatial HAC standard errors for linear fixed effects
    panel models and cross-sectional models estimated using felm().
    The spatial path uses score accumulation, latitude/longitude candidate
    pruning, and CSR neighbor lists instead of dense distance matrices,
    yielding large speedups over rbluhm/conley on big cross-sections and
    high-dimensional regressions.
License: MIT
Encoding: UTF-8
